                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Uriel.L/">[已注销]</a>
                    <span>2011-11-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">如果不能洞察人性，大概读什么兵书都如同在读废纸罢…</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1112689702">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1112689702" class="vote-count">1</span>
